column16: Orlando Arcia grounds out, shortstop Javier Baez to first baseman Anthony Rizzo.
Domingo Santana singles on a line drive to center fielder Ian Happ.   Eric Thames scores.    Jonathan Villar scores.  Domingo Santana advances to 2nd, on a throwing error by center fielder Ian Happ.
Travis Shaw called out on strikes.
Jonathan Villar reaches on a fielding error by left fielder Kyle Schwarber.   Jonathan Villar to 2nd.  Eric Thames advances to 3rd, on a throwing error by left fielder Kyle Schwarber.
Eric Thames singles on a line drive to center fielder Ian Happ.
